Terminator 2D: No Fate is an action video game developed by Bitmap Bureau and published by Reef Entertainment for Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Windows, Xbox One, and Xbox Series X/S. The game takes place during events of the movie, Terminator 2: Judgment Day.
